'''穆拉河'''（{{lang-en|Mula River}}）是印度[[浦那|浦那]]的一條河流，於西高止山脈附近被{{le|穆爾希水壩|Mulshi Dam}}攔截，而形成穆爾希湖<ref name="getaway">{{cite news |title=Quick getaway: Mulshi dam, Chail |url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2012-04-12/news/31331134_1_chail-mulshi-kms |date=12 April 2012 |agency=The Economic Times (India) |accessdate=7 July 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305144251/http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2012-04-12/news/31331134_1_chail-mulshi-kms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在浦那市的下游地帶，穆拉河與左側的{{le|帕瓦納河|Pawana River}}及右側的{{le|穆薩河|Mutha River}}合流，形成{{le|穆拉-穆塔河|Mula-Mutha}}，之後匯入{{le|比馬河|Bhima River}}<ref name="riversystems">{{cite book|title=GAZETTEERS OF BOMBAY STATE – POONA|url=https://cultural.maharashtra.gov.in/english/gazetteer/Poona/PART%20I/Chap(1)/River%20Systems.htm|accessdate=7 Jul 2014|publisher=Ministry of Culture and Tourism, [[Government_of_Maharashtra|Government of Maharashtra]]|chapter=RIVER SYSTEMS|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041331/https://cultural.maharashtra.gov.in/english/gazetteer/Poona/PART%20I/Chap(1)/River%20Systems.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本河流沿著{{le|舊浦那-孟買高速公路|Old Pune–Mumbai Highway}}，為{{le|賓布里金傑沃德市政公司|Pimpri-Chinchwad Municipal Corporation}}與{{le|浦那市政公司|Pune Municipal Corporation}}的界線<ref name="newbridge">{{cite news |title=Another bridge across Mula river in Dapodi planned |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/pune/Another-bridge-across-Mula-river-in-Dapodi-planned/articleshow/21471699.cms |date=30 July 2013 |agency=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]] |location=Pune |accessdate=7 July 2014 |archive-date=2018-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181029161834/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/pune/Another-bridge-across-Mula-river-in-Dapodi-planned/articleshow/21471699.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 橋樑 ==
本河流橫跨著許多橋樑。其中拉吉夫·甘地橋（{{lang|en|Rajiv Gandhi Bridge}}）橫跨於{{le|阿恩德|Aundh (Pune)}}，連結浦那與拉韋（{{lang|en|Ravet}}）<ref name="cuttrees">{{cite news |title=Pimpri-Chinchwad township cuts over 2,800 trees to widen Aundh-Ravet Road |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/flora-fauna/Pimpri-Chinchwad-township-cuts-over-2800-trees-to-widen-Aundh-Ravet-Road/articleshow/16985789.cms |first=Siddharth |last=Gaikwad |date=28 October 2012 |location=Pune|publisher=Times of India |accessdate=7 July 2014}}</ref>。哈里斯橋（{{lang|en|Harris Bridge}}）則橫跨於達坡迪（{{lang|en|Dapodi}}）<ref name="harrisbridge">{{cite news|title=17-yr-old dies after hitting pole on Harris Bridge |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/17-yr-old-dies-after-hitting-pole-on-harris-bridge/articleshow/19906123.cms |date=6 May 2013 |location=Pune|publisher=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|accessdate=7 July 2014}}</ref>。

