== 污染與洪水 ==
2010年，由於高污染物質與垃圾傾倒於穆拉河中，造成其周邊地區遭遇大洪水<ref name="wasted">{{cite news |title=Mula river ‘wasted’, get set for flash floods this monsoon |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/pune/report-mula-river-wasted-get-set-for-flash-floods-this-monsoon-1677459 |first=Partha Sarthi |last=Biswas |date=18 April 2012 |location=Pune |publisher=[[Daily_News_and_Analysis|Daily News and Analysis]] |accessdate=7 July 2014 |archive-date=2016-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406154154/http://www.dnaindia.com/pune/report-mula-river-wasted-get-set-for-flash-floods-this-monsoon-1677459 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{le|浦那工程學院|College of Engineering, Pune}}每年都會在其校址附近的穆拉河舉辦划舟比賽。2012年，他們發現該河流無法從基爾凱埃航行到學院，因為馬哈拉施特拉天然氣有限公司（{{lang|en|Maharashtra Natural Gas Limited}}）建造了泥土小路用以興建管線，造成河流阻塞<ref name="mngl" />。

2003年，有報導指稱{{le|瓦卡德|Wakad}}附近的穆拉河發現死魚。{{le|賓布里金傑沃德市政公司|Pimpri-Chinchwad Municipal Corporation}}無法判定這起河流污染的原因<ref name="deadfish">{{cite news |title=Dead fish in Mula river raise concern |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/pune/Dead-fish-in-Mula-river-raise-concern/articleshow/19119782.cms |date=22 March 2013 |agency=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]] |location=Pune |accessdate=9 July 2014 |archive-date=2021-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323221206/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/pune/Dead-fish-in-Mula-river-raise-concern/articleshow/19119782.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於因每日1.25億的未處理廢水從{{le|浦那市政公司|Pune Municipal Corporation}}排放到穆拉河中所造成的高度污染，{{le|馬哈拉施特拉污染控制局|Maharashtra Pollution Control Board}}將其水質等級列為「{{lang|en|Class-IV}}<ref name="mpcbchap5">{{Cite web|title=MAJOR SOURCES OF POLLUTION in PUNE|url=http://mpcb.gov.in/relatedtopics/CHAPTER5.pdf|publisher=[[Maharashtra_Pollution_Control_Board|Maharashtra Pollution Control Board]]|accessdate=9 July 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003519/http://mpcb.gov.in/relatedtopics/CHAPTER5.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>」。

2014年，{{le|浦那警察局|Pune Police}}發現{{le|卡拉迪|Kharadi, Pune}}的穆拉河沿岸生長出[[大麻屬|大麻]]<ref name="cannabis">{{cite news |title=More cannabis growth found on Mula-Mutha river bed |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/pune/more-cannabis-growth-found-on-mula-mutha-river-bed/ |date=2 March 2014 |agency=[[Indian_Express|Indian Express]] |location=Pune |accessdate=9 July 2014 |archive-date=2019-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190303082509/https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/pune/more-cannabis-growth-found-on-mula-mutha-river-bed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

